You're in a bathing suit.
Doesn't matter if you get dirty.

88
00:06:07,333 --> 00:06:09,708
Just take a shower.
It's not a problem--

89
00:06:09,791 --> 00:06:10,791
[SOUSUKE gasps]

90
00:06:10,875 --> 00:06:12,583
[CHIDORI] I'll show you
a bullseye!

91
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,791
[SOUSUKE grunts]

92
00:06:13,875 --> 00:06:16,666
[CROWD gasps]

93
00:06:16,750 --> 00:06:18,125
[screaming]

94
00:06:20,625 --> 00:06:21,708
That was more...

95
00:06:21,791 --> 00:06:23,583
...powerful than usual.

96
00:06:23,666 --> 00:06:25,250
Too powerful.

97
00:06:27,333 --> 00:06:29,458
Uh, Kaname...?

98
00:06:41,083 --> 00:06:45,291
[CHIDORI] Sure, I knew he was
that kind of guy, but...

99
00:06:50,875 --> 00:06:52,708
[CHIDORI] That attitude...

100
00:06:52,791 --> 00:06:55,250
He really makes it
tough to be confident...

101
00:06:55,333 --> 00:06:56,708
[WASHIO]
Excuse me.

102
00:06:57,958 --> 00:07:00,625
Are you busy young lady?

103
00:07:00,708 --> 00:07:02,500
Care to go for a cup of tea?

104
00:07:02,583 --> 00:07:04,250
Oh, uh, no-- no thanks.

105
00:07:04,333 --> 00:07:06,083
Uh, I'm really
not that kind of--

106
00:07:06,166 --> 00:07:07,625
[WASHIO]
Please, reconsider.

107
00:07:07,708 --> 00:07:10,791
If you refuse my offer, I'll be
forced to disembowel myself.

108
00:07:10,875 --> 00:07:12,333
[CHIDORI laughs nervously]

109
00:07:12,416 --> 00:07:14,833
That's quite a unique pickup
line. It's pretty funny, but--

110
00:07:14,916 --> 00:07:17,541
The truth of the matter is
I prefer men who are more--

111
00:07:17,625 --> 00:07:18,541
Well, how do I put this?

112
00:07:18,625 --> 00:07:19,583
Um... slender.

113
00:07:19,666 --> 00:07:21,000
[WASHIO]
Then there isn't a problem! 

114
00:07:21,083 --> 00:07:23,208
My master happens to be slender.

115
00:07:23,291 --> 00:07:24,291
Master?

116
00:07:24,375 --> 00:07:26,375
[WASHIO]
Yes, he's waiting over there.

117
00:07:26,458 --> 00:07:29,833
He has instructed me to tell
you he'd love to meet you.

118
00:07:32,416 --> 00:07:34,250
[KYOKO]
Mizuki? Pass the salt.

119
00:07:34,333 --> 00:07:35,458
[MIZUKI]
Here ya go.

120
00:07:35,541 --> 00:07:37,041
[SHINJI] This
watermelon's delicious, huh?

121
00:07:37,125 --> 00:07:39,916
[REN] Mr. Kazuma, we're
saving that for Ms. Chidori.

122
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,250
[SHINJI]
Okay!

123
00:07:41,333 --> 00:07:43,708
Yeah, speaking of which,
she hasn't come back yet.

124
00:07:43,791 --> 00:07:45,541
Yes, that's quite
a long shower

125
00:07:45,625 --> 00:07:47,875
for simply washing off some
watermelon juice.

126
00:07:49,041 --> 00:07:51,208
Are you saying that
because you believe it?

127
00:07:51,291 --> 00:07:53,291
What do you mean?

128
00:07:53,375 --> 00:07:55,625
Souskue, you mean
you really don't know?

129
00:07:57,583 --> 00:07:59,041
[SOUSUKE]
A traffic accident...

130
00:07:59,125 --> 00:08:00,375
Sudden illness...

131
00:08:00,458 --> 00:08:02,208
Stepping on a land mine...

132
00:08:02,291 --> 00:08:04,666
Finding and trailing
an old enemy...

133
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:06,375
And kidnapping...

134
00:08:06,458 --> 00:08:08,833
The most likely option is...

135
00:08:08,916 --> 00:08:10,875
--Ah! The landmine!
--No, stupid.

136
00:08:10,958 --> 00:08:12,125
Kaname's mad at you.

137
00:08:12,208 --> 00:08:14,125
I mean, we're also
partly to blame,

138
00:08:14,208 --> 00:08:15,791
but you're the one
primarily at fault

139
00:08:15,875 --> 00:08:17,416
and you're the one
she's really mad at.

140
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:20,333
So you should be the one to
go out and try to find her.

141
00:08:20,416 --> 00:08:22,500
All right. I'll do it.

142
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,750
I wonder if he
really gets it...?

143
00:08:25,833 --> 00:08:27,916
He really is such a dimwit.

144
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,208
I hope they can reach
a reconcilliation...

145
00:08:30,291 --> 00:08:33,416
[MIZUKI]
Meh, leave them alone.

146
00:08:33,500 --> 00:08:35,833
[CHIDORI]
Whooaaa...

147
00:08:35,916 --> 00:08:39,291
Places that have money
really have money.

148
00:08:39,375 --> 00:08:40,375
[WASHIO]
This way, please.

149
00:08:40,458 --> 00:08:42,625
Oh! Right...

150
00:08:42,708 --> 00:08:43,708
Hey, hey!

151
00:08:43,791 --> 00:08:44,958
What do you think you're doing?!

152
00:08:45,041 --> 00:08:47,000
C'mon, get down from here!

153
00:08:47,083 --> 00:08:48,541
You'll get me in trouble.

154
00:08:59,208 --> 00:09:01,416
[CHIDORI]
Just how big is this place?

155
00:09:09,958 --> 00:09:12,125
[WASHIO]
Now, please wait one moment.

156
00:09:23,958 --> 00:09:25,958
Whoa...

157
00:09:27,041 --> 00:09:32,791
So this is... a real
rich person's place...

158
00:09:33,708 --> 00:09:35,833
[MASATAMI]
This is... really real! 

159
00:09:35,916 --> 00:09:36,666
[CHIDORI growls]

160
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:38,125
[MASATAMI yells]

161
00:09:41,833 --> 00:09:43,125
Yes, it's real!

162
00:09:43,208 --> 00:09:44,958
I-I'm truly sorry.

163
00:09:45,041 --> 00:09:47,041
I was just so incredibly happy.

164
00:09:47,125 --> 00:09:50,250
I forgot myself for a moment.

165
00:09:50,333 --> 00:09:51,625
Who are you?

166
00:09:51,708 --> 00:09:53,625
I am Masatami Hyuga.

167
00:09:53,708 --> 00:09:55,541
Please, forgive me
for bringing you here

168
00:09:55,625 --> 00:09:57,791
in such an ungracious manner.

169
00:09:57,875 --> 00:09:59,958
Normally, I would
have certainly

170
00:10:00,041 --> 00:10:02,041
extended an invitation
to you in person

171
00:10:02,125 --> 00:10:05,041
but my doctor hasn't been
allowing me to leave the house.

172
00:10:05,125 --> 00:10:07,208
So I've been convalescing here.

173
00:10:07,291 --> 00:10:10,000
[CHIDORI] You mean, you're
the master of this house?

174
00:10:10,083 --> 00:10:11,750
[MASATAMI]
Yes...

175
00:10:11,833 --> 00:10:13,458
[CHIDORI]
Frail rich boys...

176
00:10:13,541 --> 00:10:15,458
They really do exist.

177
00:10:15,541 --> 00:10:17,791
I'm sure that this
sudden series of events

178
00:10:17,875 --> 00:10:20,625
has been very perplexing
for you, but if you like,

179
00:10:20,708 --> 00:10:23,125
would you care to
have a cup of tea?

180
00:10:23,208 --> 00:10:26,083
Well, I... I don't
know about that.

181
00:10:26,166 --> 00:10:28,083
[MASATAMI whimpers]

182
00:10:28,166 --> 00:10:30,583
[CHIDORI]
Wow, he's cute!

183
00:10:30,666 --> 00:10:34,625
Mmm... sure, I will
take that cup of tea!

184
00:10:34,708 --> 00:10:36,500
[MASATAMI] Really? Thank you!

185
00:10:36,583 --> 00:10:39,000
I'll have someone
prepare it right away.

186
00:10:39,083 --> 00:10:40,708
But, umm...

187
00:10:40,791 --> 00:10:43,916
Kaname. I'm Kaname Chidori.

188
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:48,375
[MASATAMI] M-Ms. Kaname? Ah...
What a beautifully elegant name.

189
00:10:48,458 --> 00:10:50,375
Like a quiet,
unassuming slug,

190
00:10:50,458 --> 00:10:52,541
the sound of your name
crawls into my ears

191
00:10:52,625 --> 00:10:53,500
and soothes my soul.

192
00:10:53,583 --> 00:10:54,666
Eew, a slug...

193
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:57,375
[WASHIO]
Pardon me, Master Masatami.

194
00:10:57,458 --> 00:10:58,500
[MASATAMI]
Yes, Washio?

195
00:10:58,583 --> 00:11:00,125
[WASHIO]
You have a visitor.

196
00:11:00,208 --> 00:11:02,875
He's saying something
about receiving intelligence

197
00:11:02,958 --> 00:11:06,083
that a girl named Kaname
Chidori must be here.

198
00:11:06,166 --> 00:11:07,708
--What shall I do?
--[CHIDORI] Sousuke?

199
00:11:07,791 --> 00:11:08,958
[MASATAMI]
Is he a friend of yours?

200
00:11:09,041 --> 00:11:10,666
Huh? Mmm...

201
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,125
He's, uh...

202
00:11:13,666 --> 00:11:15,208
[MASATAMI]
Ms. Kaname?

203
00:11:15,291 --> 00:11:17,833
He-He's nothing but
a sick pervert!

204
00:11:17,916 --> 00:11:20,541
