209
00:11:30,541 --> 00:11:31,833
[WASHIO]
As you wish.

210
00:11:31,916 --> 00:11:33,958
[WASHIO] There is no one
fitting this description.

211
00:11:34,041 --> 00:11:35,666
[SOUSUKE]
Please check one more time.

212
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:39,833
She's a 16-year-old Japanese
female just over 165 cm tall.

213
00:11:39,916 --> 00:11:42,041
Long hair wearing a
white bathing suit.

214
00:11:42,125 --> 00:11:43,833
Physically fit with
an ideal physiuqe.

215
00:11:43,916 --> 00:11:45,000
Never given birth.

216
00:11:45,083 --> 00:11:46,791
Accessories for today
are a red ribbon,

217
00:11:46,875 --> 00:11:47,875
colored and manicured nails--

218
00:11:47,958 --> 00:11:50,375
[WASHIO]
She isn't here. Please leave.

219
00:12:09,291 --> 00:12:10,958
[ALL]
She's been captured?

220
00:12:11,041 --> 00:12:13,208
[SOUSUKE] Correct. Though I
don't have the full details,

221
00:12:13,291 --> 00:12:14,583
that much is certain.

222
00:12:14,666 --> 00:12:17,333
