224
00:12:19,291 --> 00:12:22,250
Isn't this just another
one of your mix-ups.

225
00:12:22,333 --> 00:12:23,875
[SOUSUKE]
Wishful thinking is deadly.

226
00:12:23,958 --> 00:12:25,916
If we just stand
idly by, then she--

227
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:30,750
[CHIDORI]
Ahh! Please! No! Stop, stop!

228
00:12:30,833 --> 00:12:32,250
Damn scumbags.

229
00:12:32,333 --> 00:12:34,791
Sousuke, you're not thinking of
something real dirty now,

230
00:12:34,875 --> 00:12:35,458
are you?

231
00:12:35,541 --> 00:12:37,000
[SOUSUKE]
Chidori!

232
00:12:37,083 --> 00:12:38,291
Don't die...

233
00:12:43,583 --> 00:12:45,875
[CHIDORI]
Mmm. It's good.

234
00:12:45,958 --> 00:12:49,166
[MASATAMI] Oh, I'm truly
pleased that you enjoy it.

235
00:12:49,250 --> 00:12:50,791
[CHIDORI]
This is really great.

236
00:12:50,875 --> 00:12:54,375
[seagulls cawing]

237
00:12:54,458 --> 00:12:56,416
[CHIDORI]
And this view here!

238
00:13:02,750 --> 00:13:06,875
[CHIDORI] Sousuke, I wonder
what he's doing now.

239
00:13:06,958 --> 00:13:09,041
Something the matter,
Miss Kaname?

240
00:13:09,125 --> 00:13:12,333
What? Oh, no.
I was just thinking.

241
00:13:12,416 --> 00:13:14,458
[MASATAMI] If you're concerned
about that pervert,

242
00:13:14,541 --> 00:13:16,375
there's nothing for
you to worry about.

243
00:13:16,458 --> 00:13:18,500
This mansion is
guarded on all fronts

